        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3547010424" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12658997135730928678">I generally like reading books about US presidents and Franklin Roosevelt is one of the more interesting presidents to read about but I didnt find this book very interesting for the most part. There were interesting moments but then the book seemed to drag. Maybe too small of a focus for such a large book. But just the idea of two world leaders getting along so well when in this day and age there seems to be so much dissension was nice to think about. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


